---
import ContactHeroImage from '../assets/blog-placeholder-about.jpg';
import Layout from '../layouts/BlogPost.astro';
---

<Layout
    title="Contact Us"
    description="Бидэнтэй холбоо барих"
    pubDate={new Date('July 14 2025')}
    heroImage={ContactHeroImage}
>
    <h2>Холбоо барих</h2>
    <p>
        Та доорх формыг ашиглан бидэнд хүсэлт, санал, асуултаа илгээж болно.
    </p>
    <form class="contact-form" method="post">
        <label>
            Нэр:
            <input type="text" name="name" required />
        </label>
        <label>
            Имэйл:
            <input type="email" name="email" required />
        </label>
        <label>
            Мессеж:
            <textarea name="message" rows="5" required></textarea>
        </label>
        <button type="submit">Илгээх</button>
    </form>
</Layout>

<style>
.contact-form {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1em;
    max-width: 400px;
    margin: 2em auto 0 auto;
}
.contact-form label {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    font-weight: 500;
    gap: 0.3em;
}
.contact-form input,
.contact-form textarea {
    padding: 0.5em;
    border: 1px solid #ccc;
    border-radius: 4px;
    font-size: 1em;
}
.contact-form button {
    background: var(--accent, #4f46e5);
    color: #fff;
    border: none;
    padding: 0.7em 1.5em;
    border-radius: 4px;
    font-size: 1em;
    cursor: pointer;
    font-weight: 600;
    transition: background 0.2s;
}
